thread.title: Roscommon93

author: Roscommon93
title: Roscommon93
text: A joke of an insurance company. 3 notices and your policy gets cancelled even though they give you very little notice when your kilometres get low. The bonus kilometres never happen and the support services are terrible. Cheap insurance at the beginning and then you have to top up when the kilometres go low so you're spending as much topping up as you would have buying insurance with a better company . Would never insure with these again
